boosting physical power up to 3.88 times higher than normal and enabling high speed movement.

I will pretend to panic as I hurtle toward the wall,
and then stop a second before my death!

he said that just passing should not be enough.

I do not care that much.

and he said you should totally go and peek!

so if you want to match the class average, you will need to study very hard.
Okay, then let us get started.

What is the probability that the sum of the rolls will be three?

I thought that if I could understand the person behind the dice roll I could work it out,
but it is a lot harder to guess what he is thinking than I thought!
So this is all you can do?
I have yet to unleash my full potential.

Okay then, let us start from a bit earlier.

Why are you arguing with me?
I will be able to work seriously after a break!
I will make you tea as well!
Your sister is not home yet?
What would you like to drink?

You were just too embarrassed to say thanks?

I have not changed it since junior high...
I am changing it right now, so wait a moment.
You should be able to come up with something great.
I think your current one's just fine.
Then I am using your code.
But can you really just change it like that?
You know, if you change it, you will have to tell all your junior high friends and your family...
It should be fine if I just tell the Priestess and Dekomori.
In this dimension, they are the only ones who acknowledge my existence.
But if you come up with a new code for me,

I will teach you as much as I can until the exams.

I figured I would just be disturbing you, so I left.
Now it is over between us.
